---
title: Herby Pan-Seared Chicken with Farro Caprese Salad
description: We’ve created a new fusion cuisine for lunch or dinner: French + Italian = Fritalian! Jokes aside, we were shocked by how much we loved the combination of Herbs de Provence and Caprese salad. We think you’ll love it too!
